        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="hero-tag">Data Visualization Project ¬∑ LSE ¬∑ 2026</p>
            <h1>No One's Land</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Power vacuums, armed groups and deforestation before and after Colombia's 2016 Peace Agreement</p>
        </div>
        <span class="hero-credit">Image: Renaldo Matamoro in Unsplash</a>
