                        <p class="source-meta">Web scraping for per-capita normalization of conflict data ‚Äî <a href="https://www.dane.gov.co/" target="_blank">dane.gov.co</a></p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="source-header">
                            <strong>Geographic Boundaries</strong>
